## üìà Model Details

- **Model type:** Logistic regression (`glm`)
- **Framework:** `tidymodels`
- **Features include:**
  - Plate appearances
  - wOBA / xwOBA
  - Average & max exit velocity
  - Barrel rate
  - Sweet spot %
  - EV95%

- **Target:**  
  Binary breakout indicator (top 20% ŒîwOBA within season)

- **Evaluation:**
  - ROC AUC
  - Decile-based calibration plot

